caller_intent: Cancel insurance on a 2020 Honda Civic and confirm the impact on the policy's premium.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the vehicle details (2020 Honda Civic) and other vehicles on the policy (78 Chevy K10, 23 Honda CRV, 2003 Chevy Impala).
Agent processed the cancellation of the Honda Civic.
Agent provided a premium estimate: old premium $3,711, new premium $2,462, with a $550.90 refund.
Agent reminded caller to return the license tag to BNV to avoid issues.
knowledge_required: BNV (likely Bureau of Motor Vehicles or similar agency) tag return requirements
systems_referenced: Lawrence Insurance internal system for policy management and premium calculation
summary: Jamie assisted Jacob in canceling insurance on his 2020 Honda Civic, confirmed remaining vehicles on the policy, and provided a premium adjustment estimate. The agent emphasized returning the license tag to BNV. The call concluded with Jacob satisfied and no further action needed.
